  <title>Lupine Science — Unlocking the materials that build the future</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Intelligence became abundant; verified knowledge did not. Lupine Science makes AI's predictions of new materials provable — mathematics a computer checks, evidence anyone can audit — so discovery stops waiting on guesswork.">
